        "features": [],
        "columns": 3,
        "items": [
          {
            "icon": "Star",
            "title": {
              "zh": "Mastery of Authentic Heavyweight Fabrics",
              "en": "Mastery of Authentic Heavyweight Fabrics"
            },
            "description": {
              "zh": "American streetwear culture places a premium on the \"hand-feel\" and structural integrity of a garment. Kellogg Fashion specializes in high-GSM (Grams per Square Meter) fabrics, often ranging from 400 GSM to over 500 GSM. Unlike standard suppliers, Kellogg’s textiles are engineered to be \"stiff\" and \"dense\" rather than just thick, providing the rugged, high-end aesthetic that US consumers associate with luxury streetwear brands.",
              "en": "American streetwear culture places a premium on the \"hand-feel\" and structural integrity of a garment. Kellogg Fashion specializes in high-GSM (Grams per Square Meter) fabrics, often ranging from 400 GSM to over 500 GSM. Unlike standard suppliers, Kellogg’s textiles are engineered to be \"stiff\" and \"dense\" rather than just thick, providing the rugged, high-end aesthetic that US consumers associate with luxury streetwear brands."
            }
          },
          {
            "icon": "Star",
            "title": {
              "zh": "Precision in American \"Boxy\" Silhouettes",
              "en": "Precision in American \"Boxy\" Silhouettes"
            },
            "description": {
              "zh": "The US market has moved away from slim or standard European cuts toward a very specific \"Boxy Fit.\" This includes dropped shoulders, cropped body lengths, and wide sleeves. Kellogg Fashion has developed a deep library of pre-vetted patterns that specifically cater to this aesthetic. By providing \"brand-ready\" silhouettes, they allow American labels to skip the long, expensive process of multiple sampling rounds to get the fit right.",
              "en": "The US market has moved away from slim or standard European cuts toward a very specific \"Boxy Fit.\" This includes dropped shoulders, cropped body lengths, and wide sleeves. Kellogg Fashion has developed a deep library of pre-vetted patterns that specifically cater to this aesthetic. By providing \"brand-ready\" silhouettes, they allow American labels to skip the long, expensive process of multiple sampling rounds to get the fit right."
            }
          },
          {
            "icon": "Star",
            "title": {
              "zh": "Agile Manufacturing for \"Drop\" Culture",
              "en": "Agile Manufacturing for \"Drop\" Culture"
            },
            "description": {
              "zh": "The modern American fashion business model relies heavily on the \"Drop\" system—releasing limited quantities frequently to maintain hype. Kellogg Fashion offers a flexible, low-MOQ (Minimum Order Quantity) framework that is highly attractive to both boutique labels and scaling brands. This agility allows American companies to test new colors and designs with minimal inventory risk, moving from a creative concept to a physical sample in as little as 7 to 10 days.",
              "en": "The modern American fashion business model relies heavily on the \"Drop\" system—releasing limited quantities frequently to maintain hype. Kellogg Fashion offers a flexible, low-MOQ (Minimum Order Quantity) framework that is highly attractive to both boutique labels and scaling brands. This agility allows American companies to test new colors and designs with minimal inventory risk, moving from a creative concept to a physical sample in as little as 7 to 10 days."
            }
          },
          {
            "icon": "Star",
            "title": {
              "zh": "Seamless End-to-End Export Expertise",
              "en": "Seamless End-to-End Export Expertise"
            },
            "description": {
              "zh": "International sourcing can be a logistical nightmare regarding customs, duties, and shipping times. Kellogg Fashion has established a robust export infrastructure specifically for the North American market. By offering transparent communication and professional logistics solutions—such as DDP (Delivered Duty Paid) shipping—they function as a \"plug-and-play\" backend for US brands, allowing founders to focus on marketing and community building while the production is handled with professional reliability.",
              "en": "International sourcing can be a logistical nightmare regarding customs, duties, and shipping times. Kellogg Fashion has established a robust export infrastructure specifically for the North American market. By offering transparent communication and professional logistics solutions—such as DDP (Delivered Duty Paid) shipping—they function as a \"plug-and-play\" backend for US brands, allowing founders to focus on marketing and community building while the production is handled with professional reliability."
            }
          }
